        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "3211776"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Meer oefenen",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/a/ade70d345beb9e21aee9893cea8faa40f83d665d.png\" class=\"height-292-pixels width-250-pixels float-right\"/>Het is slim om nog meer te oefenen met Unity. Unity heeft zelf heel nuttige tutorials waar je ontzettend veel van kunt leren. (Deze zijn wel engels talig maar wel heel duidelijjk!).</p>\n<p><strong>Ik vind het moeilijk</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://unity3d.com/learn/tutorials/projects/roll-ball-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\">Doe de roll-a-ball tutorial</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Ik kom er goed uit</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://unity3d.com/learn/tutorials/projects/space-shooter-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\">Doe de space shooter tutorial</a></li>\n<li>Let op: <a href=\"https://oc.unity3d.com/index.php/s/rna2inqWBBysn6l\" target=\"_blank\">neem ook de aanpassingen door voor Unity 5 bij deze tutorial</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Ik wil meer gaan doen met graphics</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Kijk op de pagina over <a href=\"http://unity3d.com/learn/tutorials/topics/graphics\" target=\"_blank\">graphics in Unity</a></li>\n<li>Neem tutorials door over shading en lighting.</li>\n<li>Ook <a href=\"http://unity3d.com/learn/tutorials/topics/animation\" target=\"_blank\">animatie in Unity</a> is interessant.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Ik wil meer gaan doen met geluid</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Neem de pagina door over <a href=\"http://unity3d.com/learn/tutorials/topics/audio\" target=\"_blank\">geluid in Unity</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": []
        },
        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "3211778"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Entertainmentgame",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p>Voor je entertainmentgame kun je verschillende dingen nodig hebben.</p>\n<p>Bepaal of je een 2d-game maakt met sprites of een 3d-game met 3d-objecten.</p>\n<h4>2D-game development met Unity</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://unity3d.com/learn/tutorials/projects/2d-roguelike-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\">2D-tutorial</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLq3pyCh4J1B2va_ftIthSpUaQH0LycRA-\" width=\"560\" class=\"video-item\"/></div>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/f/fe147d5ba8ba49fbaede997f4c7c0c4c9c802020.png\">Spriteset speler</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/2/2b0ef0a22fc835104025797d0248063720c21f02.png\">Sprite platform</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Tanks tutorial</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://unity3d.com/learn/tutorials/projects/tanks-tutorial\">Tanks tutorial</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Blender tutorial</h4>\n<p> </p>\n<div><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLIb2EgU4-1ga5iWLPE-7tx3uUCwhPDON3\" width=\"560\" class=\"video-item\"/></div>\n<p> </p>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": []
        }
